items.name: Aiden
items.description: Aiden, the youngest pilot, embodies a rare blend of prideful innocence and surprisingly mature demeanor. Despite his tender age, he navigates the virtual skies with confidence and clarity, occasionally expressing his emotions through a complaining tone. Riding a small airplane, he adds a dash of adventurous spirit to the captivating journey of travelers.

items.name: Alphonse
items.description: Alphonse is a gentle and affectionate old man. He's familiar and informal.

items.name: Anna
items.description: Anna is a kind and gentle. She has a cute and lovely tone with a high voice.

items.name: Arin
items.description: Arin is a girl with a shy demeanor and a deep affinity for magic. She possesses a quiet strength, despite her introverted nature. Arin finds solace in magic and possesses a rich inner world of creativity and curiosity. While trying to be gentle and kind-hearted, she struggles to express herself fully.

items.name: Bert
items.description: Bert is a sinister grandfather. He has a dynamic tone.
